Karyakram

Sanjay Gokhale // 20 December 2022

Ut Labore et Dolore

कार्यक्रम

  1. त्या कोवळ्या फुलांचा - अनिल कांबळे - कविता वाचन
  2. Kavita Eka Nirakushachi - Sudhir Moghe - शाल्मली गोखले, डॉ. विक्रांत महाजन, डॉ. अश्लेषा महाजन- कविता वाचन
  3. Nakshatranche Divas (druckshravya) - Aruk Kakatkar - निवेदन
  4. Swara Saurabh (hindi - marathi lokapriya gani) Jayashree Kulkarni, Dayanad Ghotkar - निवेदन
  5. आर्त मोहिनी लता (Madan Mohan) - Aparna Sant, Shruti Devasthali, Reshma Kapshikar - निवेदन
  6. Anandaghan (Bharatratna Lata Mangeshkar) - Chaitrali Abhyankar, Aparna Sant, Hemant Walunjkar - निवेदन
  7. Kanchansandhya (Kavi Ba Bha Borkar) - Chaitrali Abhyankar, Aparna Sant, Dr. Chandrashekhar Kulkarni - निवेदन
  8. Chalavinaara Tu - Bhakti Sangeet - Ashutosh Kulkarni, Aparna Kelkar, Asawari Deglurkar - निवेदन
  9. Bhakti Sangeet (Shree Gondawle) - Sangeetkar Gayak Arun Saraf - निवेदन
  10. Pandit Jitendra Abhisheki Shruti Mahotsav - Devaki Pandit, Raja Kale, Gauri Pathare, Sudhir Nayak - निवेदन
  11. Kavi Grace (druckshravya) - Deenayan Kala Parva - कविता वाचन
  12. Goojagoshti (Na si Phadke, Vi Sa Khandekar) - Setumancha - Geetanjali Joshi, Deepali Datar, Mukund Datar, Dilip Limaye -अभिवाचन
  13. Sahitya Gangechya Kathi (Na Si Phadke - Sahitya Yatra) - Geetanjali Joshi, Deepali Datar, Anirudha Dadke - अभिवाचन
  14. Me… yesuvahini - Samidha, Pune - Veena Gokhale, Sangeeta Thosar, Dilip Thosar, Dr. Chitralekha Purandare - अभिवाचन
  15. Avasache Chandine (Mumbai Doordarshan) - Sant Shreshta Dnyaneshwer Mahrajhynachya विराण्या - Anjali Marathi, Yogita Godbole, Amruta Gokhale, Dr. Vandana Bokil - निवेदन
  16. Putra Sangati (Ga di Ma, Ram Kadam) - Shreedhar Madgulkar, VIjay Kadam - निवेदन
  17. Hidi Marathi Lokapriya Gaani - Paricharika Din - Deenayan Kala parva - Rajesh Datar, Pradnya Deshpande - निवेदन
  18. Laviyale Nandadeep (Maniv Verma) - Deenayan Kala parva - Aparna Sant - निवेदन
  19. Athvanitli Gaani - Rahul Ghorpade, Bhagyashree Abhyankar - निवेदन
